title: iBPMN Fault Handling Extension
description: A basic extension of iBPMN containing fault handling capabilities (i.e. silent/no actions, scopes, FCT handling, non-cancellation behavior using non-interrupting events).

stencils.title: Silent/no-Action Activity
stencils.description: A silent/no-Action activity that hides the details about its actual implementation.

properties.title: Status
properties.description: The Status of an activity is determined when the activity is being executed by a process engine.

properties.title: St_LoopConditionLanguage
properties.description: A language may be provided so that the syntax of the loop condition can be understood.
